Instructions
- this is a python using pyglet app
- all codes and subfolders reside on the ../src folder.
- unit test should be created for important methods and flow.
- create a simple python simulation app using pyglet.
- all required packages must be added in the reqirements.txt in the #root_folder
- the requirements is specifically listed in the following files:
    > layout = contains the general layout of the app screen and should be executed first
    > entities = contains specific instructions for every entities in the app and should be executed after layout
    > logic = contains the specific instruction for the business logic, how each entities interact as well as other rules, and should be executed after entities
    > fix_prompts = contains implementation fixes and compatibility adjustments, and should be executed last after layout, entities, and logic